verbose_text: Common problems encountered are issues related to loss of space due to migration of adjacent teeth into the available space [XREF_BIBR]; traumatic bite on opposing teeth that lead to gum recession and mobility of teeth [XREF_BIBR]; and attrition of enamel surface of the opposing teeth in contact [XREF_BIBR].
